{"tid":1512180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[職業 - 滅煙隊] 致力捍衛無煙環境","createTime":"2019-08-27T18:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T15:38:21.000Z","uid":163604,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"a653e4b46d099715777ae686e23ee21da190f48e","tid":1512180,"uid":163604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:55:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">控煙辦公海tg: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HTRM7kTc_gHF5Q_X0ThaTw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHTRM7kTc_gHF5Q_X0ThaTw&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=ab334e1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HTRM7kTc_gHF5Q_X0ThaTw</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">大家好 我地係「控煙辦」 認住螢光水袋 專做滅煙工作<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7WyAxwF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7WyAxwF.jpg&h=dfd7b6d5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地有一套tg落地即熄煙既手法<br />\n<br />\n我地相信前線需要分工合作，組織起有食過煙既手足，用高效方法（執蛋放入水袋，秒殺tg維繫0煙環境）去專心處理煙<br />\n<br />\n先前有post講既「偽前線」一枝水走去控煙 做消防<br />\n應該係被我地稱為「新手消防」/「freelance消防」既和理非<br />\n<br />\n不少人係第一次出手，需要時間成長，不需太苛刻，我地公海現正大力招募新手並教育，希望各位幫推十次&quot;光復香港 時代革命&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[控煙辦]準則:<br />\n1，高效滅煙<br />\n2，指揮身邊人企鬆一手位<br />\n3，注意防暴陣前tg唔好執<br />\n</span><br />\n不完美，可商量，可改善<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">滅火裝備（由頭到腳）<br />\n<br />\n1)⛑ 頭盔<br />\n2)🥽泳鏡優先(w/wo度數) 》眼罩密封<br />\n3)雙嘴 filter 有攻略圖<br />\n4)包頸<br />\n5)長袖/冰袖/保鮮紙密封<br />\n6)有肩帶 瑩光防水袋 (深水埗街邊3/5L)<br />\n7）🧤燒銲手套(optional) <br />\n8）👖長褲<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">新手：<br />\n5-10條 中毛巾 (越大越厚越好)<br />\n<br />\n1）準備好兩條濕毛巾在手&gt;留意槍聲<br />\n2）兩條濕毛巾掟落地蓋住粒蛋<br />\n3)  用腳踩 幾野</span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">進階/經驗老鬼：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">勇武：掟返過去（只限第一排）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">高手：手執入水袋 chok幾野，熄煙 (目前隊內主流做法)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">神手：急凍噴霧（稀有）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyMe7vh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcyMe7vh.jpg&h=1db47c32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3TCU7vF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3TCU7vF.jpg&h=e34a7442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深水埗福田商場賣 防水袋  <br />\n深水埗 毛巾勁平 大條15蚊 剪成兩條<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">控煙辦公海tg: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HTRM7kTc_gHF5Q_X0ThaTw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHTRM7kTc_gHF5Q_X0ThaTw&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=ab334e1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HTRM7kTc_gHF5Q_X0ThaTw</a></span><br />\n<br />\n快啲加入我地啦! 閒日吹水 weekend打機!"},{"pid":"c972342f2c61885462fa3a159e6415714ffda215","tid":1512180,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:56:00.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"de1a787e00623cf614cd90cce021b8368d74f61b","tid":1512180,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:56:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"40fb0ef9c37ed16b4c0ffc74a7e87c954ef06b6b","tid":1512180,"uid":98993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:56:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75f72d11e4788d02d7f6fc15287755ad39f456b8","tid":1512180,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:56:40.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"80cf70f35c4b368383d7ecd548629c984d534c55","tid":1512180,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:56:50.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a6cbf858ebc6958c87f97bb182fd25898abbf557","tid":1512180,"uid":265298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:56:54.000Z","msg":"我見過有手足用鹽樽<br />\n想問佢地又算唔算係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":