新手並教育，希望各位幫推十次&quot;光復香港 時代革命&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[控煙辦]準則:<br />\n1，高效滅煙<br />\n2，指揮身邊人企鬆一手位<br />\n3，注意防暴陣前tg唔好執<br />\n</span><br />\n不完美，可商量，可改善<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">滅火裝備（由頭到腳）<br />\n<br />\n1)⛑ 頭盔<br />\n2)🥽泳鏡優先(w/wo度數) 》眼罩密封<br />\n3)雙嘴 filter 有攻略圖<br />\n4)包頸<br />\n5)長袖/冰袖/保鮮紙密封<br />\n6)有肩帶 瑩光防水袋 (深水埗街邊3/5L)<br />\n7）🧤燒銲手套(optional) <br />\n8）👖長褲<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">新手：<br />\n5-10條 中毛巾 (越大越厚越好)<br />\n<br />\n1）準備好兩條濕毛巾在手&gt;留意槍聲<br />\n2）兩條濕毛巾掟落地蓋住粒蛋<br />\n3)  用腳踩 幾野</span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">進階/經驗老鬼：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">勇武：掟返過去（只限第一排）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">高手：手執入水袋 chok幾野，熄煙 (目前隊內主流做法)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">神手：急凍噴霧（稀有）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyMe7vh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcyMe7vh.jpg&h=1db47c32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3TCU7vF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3TCU7vF.jpg&h=e34a7442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深水埗福田商場賣 防水袋  <br />\n深水埗 毛巾勁平 大條15蚊 剪成兩條<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">控煙辦公海tg: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HTRM7kTc_gHF5Q_X0ThaTw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHTRM7kTc_gHF5Q_X0ThaTw&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=ab334e1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HTRM7kTc_gHF5Q_X0ThaTw</a></span><br />\n<br />\n快啲加入我地啦! 閒日吹水 weekend打機!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T22:38:14.000Z","msg":"面擋呢？槍槍打頭想攞命！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:35:53.000Z","msg":"有裝"},{"pid":"8bed0e2cc47c79bb7a7546fa3e72872f372455c2","tid":1512180,"uid":274248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:41:30.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"bb3349e0ec3b266